<title>HE LEADETH ME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I Pathien in ei pui zel hi,
 Tih ka hetin ka kipak hi;
 Bang semin, khawiah um mahleng,
 Pathien khut in ei pui zel hi.

[V2]
 Ei pui zel hi! ei pui zel hi!
 Amah khut in ei pui zel hi;
 A nungzui ginum hih ka nuom,
 Amah khut in ei pui zel hi.

[V3]
 2. Abangkuom leh ka lungkham in,
 Abangkuom leh ka kipak hi;
 Mun lauh-um leh muonna mun ah,
 Pathien khut in ei pui zel hi.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa, ka khut in hun tu'ng ka,
 Phunchiek leh nuok a umlo in;
 Ka thilneih phawt ah lungawi ka,
 Pathien khut in ei puih ziek in.

[V5]
 4. Lei a ka nasep ka zawh tieng,
 Lungsiet vang' guolzo ka hih tieng;
 Thihna lauh-umna lau puo'ng ka,
 Jordan nei puihkaihding ziek in.</lyrics>
</song>